summary: [SPOILERS] Final season who will be raised from the dead?
title: [SPOILERS] Final season who will be raised from the dead?
body:
So if the night king is raising white walkers left right and centre who will he bring back during the grand finale? I have always kept an eye out for a zombie Hodor. If they make it to Kings Landing where the royal tombs are do we reckon we might see a white walker version of King Bobby B swinging his hammer? A headless Ned? What are the implications of a Targeryen white walker and are they immune to fire?



Source: https://ift.tt/2NGQIKa

summary: [NO SPOILERS] Just out of curiosity, how do y'all usually watch Game Of Thrones?
title: [NO SPOILERS] Just out of curiosity, how do y'all usually watch Game Of Thrones?
body:
I usually watch it with a couple friends who are big fans of the show, also most of my family is into GoT so sometimes when we’re all together we re-watch some of our favorite episodes.

How do y'all usually watch it? Maybe with your wife/husband, or your entire family, maybe you like to watch it by yourself to make sure you don’t miss anything, or with friends, maybe even go to a bar or somewhere else?



Source: https://ift.tt/2MtUVw4
